data.description: Private wooded setting across from the Wisconsin River with views & convenient river access to meet all of your water recreation needs. Located on a quiet dead-end street close to two public boat launch options. This ranch home backs to conservancy acreage and has been thoughtfully updated throughout to enjoy year-round living, as a weekend getaway or a vacation rental - so many options!  Open floor plan w/vaulted ceilings & skylights. New roof & gutters in 2020, furnace and central a/c 2016, hot water heater in 2018. Crawl space provides enormous storage with easy access, lighting & power outlet. Large attic provides even more storage along with deep garage containing a shelving unit. Low taxes & absolutely nothing to do here but bring your furniture and enjoy! 30 min to Madison.
